  "texts": [
    "Hence, users have to be made aware when they are interacting with a machine so they can decide whether or not to continue using the AI system.",
    "In addition, the AI system must be designed in such a way that it prevents the generation and diffusion of illegal content.",
    "Finally, AI systems considered to be of minimal or no risk, such as many gaming apps or spam filters, will largely remain outside the scope of the AI Act.",
    "Many AI systems currently used in the EU will fall into this category.",
